    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "马戏与龙　前篇",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "很久很久以前，\\n一头幼龙和一位少年相遇了。\\n他们都有着一颗\\n找寻乐趣的心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_210043_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“今天做点什么好玩的事呢！”\\n这就是属于他们的暗号。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "你追我赶、捉迷藏、\\n对大人恶作剧……\\n有时也会想想新的游戏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "某天，少年居住的村子里\\n来了一顶色彩鲜艳的帐篷。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“这个绝对很好玩！”\\n于是他们接触到了马戏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_120017_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "空中秋千、投掷短剑、\\n驯兽，还有小丑的表演……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "眼前不断上演\\n令人眼花缭乱的表演，\\n让他们看得入神。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“马戏真是太有趣了！”\\n“我们也试试吧！”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "这便是小小的驯龙师\\n诞生的瞬间。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "在村子里的大人面前\\n表演自己想出来的节目——\\n虽然规模尚小，\\n但对少年与龙来说\\n已是非常出色的马戏表演。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "虽然规模很小\\n却很有趣的马戏表演\\n终究也会落下帷幕。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "此时的他们，\\n还未能理解\\n这早已注定的命运。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}